/-!
# Goertzel Lemma 8.18: first large `TTT` fiber, block 3

This module aggregates four 16-row component-certificate chunks for one
64-row part of the first size-512 fixed-input fiber of the `TTT`/`mode09`
representative target.
-/

namespace GoertzelLemma818TripleTauLargeFiber4Block3ComponentCertificate

open GoertzelLemma818TripleTauLargeFiber4Block3Chunk0ComponentCertificate
open GoertzelLemma818TripleTauLargeFiber4Block3Chunk1ComponentCertificate
open GoertzelLemma818TripleTauLargeFiber4Block3Chunk2ComponentCertificate
open GoertzelLemma818TripleTauLargeFiber4Block3Chunk3ComponentCertificate

def tttLargeFiber4Block3ComponentCertificateAudit : Bool :=
